description: A federal judge in Texas struck down LGBTQ protections for students after the Biden administration attempted to re-write federal law, he said.
title: Texas federal court strikes down Biden admin protections for LGBTQ students

description: Golden State Warriors head coach Steve Kerr was asked what he thinks about how Caitlin Clark has been treated by opponents in the WNBA, and he likened her to his superstar, Steph Curry.
title: Warriors' Steve Kerr likens Caitlin Clark to Steph Curry, calls her battles with WNBA vets 'rite of passage'

description: Republican Rep. Nancy Mace of South Carolina, backed by former President Trump, survives a serious primary challenge, defeating a rival who was backed by former House Speaker Kevin McCarthy.
title: Nancy Mace wins South Carolina 1st congressional district primary over Kevin McCarthy-backed challenger

description: Fox News host Laura Ingraham dissects Attorney General Merrick Garland's opinion article slamming criticism of the Justice Department on "The Ingraham Angle."
title: LAURA INGRAHAM: This is Merrick Garland's tragic comedy

description: Joey Chestnut said he is "gutted" to have learned he is "banned" from the 2024 Nathan's Hot Dog Eating Contest following a brand partnership with a rival.
title: Joey Chestnut breaks silence after learning he cannot compete in 2024 hot dog eating contest

description: Honolulu police suggested that residents and tourists alike bring their valuables into the pristine waters with them, rather then leave them on the beach, amid an uptick of crime.
title: Hawaii crime reaches new heights as police urge beachgoers to take valuables into the ocean

description: German archaeologists recently announced the discovery of millennia-old game pieces. The artifacts were found at the site of a destroyed castle and were found under debris.
title: Thousand-year-old discovery comes as 'complete surprise' to experts

description: Amazon Prime Video's "The Boys," a satirical superhero series, will run for a fifth and final season, showrunner Eric Kripke announced.
title: Amazon's 'The Boys' to end after 5 seasons

description: Rory McIlroy and his wife, Erica, have had a change of heart — just a month after filing for a divorce, the golfer says they will remain together.
title: Rory McIlroy says he and wife are not divorcing: 'A new beginning'
